{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Introduce a non-taxable lunch allowance for employees to ease financial burden",
        "additional_details": "I want the Government to require employers to provide a lunch allowance exempt from being taxed. Employees often spend \u00a35\u2013\u00a310 daily on meals, which adds up to significant costs. A non-taxable allowance would ease financial pressure, improve well-being, and promote fairness across workplaces.",
        "background": "I want the Government to introduce a law requiring all employers to provide a lunch allowance, which would be tax-exempt. We believe this would reduce financial pressure on employees, support workplace well-being, and ensure fair treatment across all industries.",
